title: Ben Dragon's - Deception I
description:
This is a supplemental Audio Lecture to Ben Dragon's book "A Manual For Humanity" and this one is called "Deception I". From what I gather, this is the first part of a series on deception.

If the rest are as good as this one is then I'll be adding them too!


Ben Dragon touches on the use of colours, the Fashion Industry, music and how they are used to steer the populace.
